node.text:
Resistance band workouts have been my go to during pregnancy. Being pregnant means listening to your body and that’s exactly what I’ve been doing. Resistance to Moderate weight & higher reps. 

Complete circuit 4 times!
1️⃣PLIE SQUATS-20 reps 
2️⃣STATIONARY LUNGES-15 reps
3️⃣SINGLE LEG RDLs-20 reps
4️⃣SIDE STEP TO SQUAT-15 reps

@bodyxbruna 🤍

36 Week Update- On my nesting vibes. Getting everything ready & I’m so excited😬 I can’t believe we are almost at the finish line. Crib gets here this week & as soon as it’s here I’m filming the nursery reveal!!! 

Might be a little TMI but I’ll share anyways… Started my morning off losing some of my mucus plug. Feeling like my belly has dropped and like she flipped 🤞🏼 I’ve been reminding myself throughout this pregnancy that everything will unfold the way God wants it to. My plan is a home birth but my hospital bag is packed incase🙏 Thank you all for your love and support means so much to my family and I 🤍

P.S. What are some of your hospital bag must haves?
